libs.content:
find_library(
    lzo_library
    names
        liblzo2.so
        liblzo2.a
        lzo2_64.lib
    hints
        ${thirdparty_libs_hints}
    path_suffixes
        ${_lib_suffixes}
)

find_library(
    tiff_library
    names
        libtiff.a
    hints
        ${sdkroot}
    path_suffixes
        tiff-4.2.0/libtiff/.libs
    no_default_path
)

find_library(
    superlu_library
    names
        libsuperlu.so
        libsuperlu.a
        libsuperlu_4.1.a
    hints
        ${thirdparty_libs_hints}
    path_suffixes
        superlu
)

deps.context:
find_package(qt5 required
    core
    gui
    network
    opengl
    svg
    xml
    script
    widgets
    printsupport
    linguisttools
    multimedia
    multimediawidgets
    serialport
    uitools
)

libs.content: find_library(openblas_lib names cblas gslcblas openblas blas)
